		screen_text = "I've lost every bit o' my sorcerin' gear and I didn't recover Phaedriel's gold. I need sumethin' I can take back to my father Radicus to shows that I'm not a complete mooncalf. If you don't have the gold I'm askin' for now, then you can finds me later.";
